title: Acid Catalysis in Modern Organic Synthesis, Vol 2
description:
Acid Catalysis in Modern Organic Synthesis, Vol 2 - Hisashi Yamamoto, Kazuaki Ishihara (Wiley-VCH, 2008).pdf

This volume focuses on different areas of acid chemistry and catalysis, whichhave been selected because they have developed significantly, and in some caseseven completely, in the last few years. Each author is very knowledgeable in hisjherparticular field of chemistry and is able to provide a valuable perspective fromthe point of view of synthesis
